{"tid":1066042,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利物浦真係好麻煩","createTime":"2019-03-17T16:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T16:17:11.000Z","uid":55091,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"983596453d53610245701e4083c6a529c64ee130","tid":1066042,"uid":55091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T16:14:18.000Z","msg":"頭先一路睇波條link斷吓斷吓<br />\n係臨三十分鐘前終於搵到條順link<br />\n就係嗰一刻 嗰個moment<br />\n我見証住利記又派膠俾人追和<br />\n每一次都係咁 當我以爲可以開心吓就會咁<br />\n但今次嘅我已經唔同咗<br />\n我即刻買咗50雞利記反cup <br />\n盡我些少嘅心血 好似無用 但起碼有試過<br />\n結果 贏咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9910147232e7d62ce58af1f90c32874b9dafd9c","tid":1066042,"uid":25100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T16:17:11.000Z","msg":"So 關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}